Package: ShennongObject
Type: Package
Title: Modern Data Structures for Multi-Omics Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Songqi", "Duan", , "duan@songqi.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0822-5883"))
  )
Description: 
  Provides a tidy, extensible, and modular S4 data infrastructure for organizing
  and analyzing multi-omics and single-cell datasets in R. The ShennongObject 
  class extends MultiAssayExperiment to support streamlined integration of assays, 
  flexible metadata management, dimensionality reductions, visualization tools, 
  and analysis provenance tracking. Designed for compatibility with tidyverse-style 
  workflows and modern bioinformatics pipelines.
